{"type": "article", "id": 8048, "title": "LEGO 黑胶唱片机", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-02T07:44:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234655iT2SIlgYPxaqA9M1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t韩国设计师 Hayarobi 是忠实的 LEGO 粉丝，他最近用 2400 块 LEGO 积木拼出了一台复古黑胶唱机，并取名为 “The Planet”。唱机整体由积木堆积而成，采用 LEGO Power Functions 8878 电池和 Power Functions 8883 M-Motor 电机供电，使得唱机可以正常运转。这台唱机前段时间入选了 2014 年首尔 Brick Pop 艺术展。不知道是不是给了同样喜欢 LEGO 的你新的启发呢？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346531FqRTPNAMEQGy6s2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55489965\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234653vyhL0xEZqoaNW9pB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61774194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346538UeV2O4IZHPBoEuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}